docs {
  # Create Vendor

  Creates a new vendor entry. If `id` is omitted, one will be auto-generated.

  ## Request Body

  ```json
  {
    "id": "new-vendor",
    "name": "New Vendor",
    "description": "A new hardware vendor",
    "website": "https://example.com"
  }
  ```

  ## Fields

  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  |-------|------|----------|-------------|
  | id | string | No | Unique identifier (auto-generated if omitted) |
  | name | string | Yes | Display name |
  | description | string | Yes | Brief description |
  | website | string | Yes | Website URL |

  ## Response

  Returns the created vendor with status `201 Created`.
}
